<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/priority/P2> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/priority> ; rdfs:label "Priority 2"@en .

<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/origin> a skos:ConceptScheme ;
    rdfs:label "Trouble Ticket Origin Concept Scheme"@en ;
