<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/urgency> a skos:ConceptScheme ;
    rdfs:label "Trouble Ticket Urgency Concept Scheme"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Controlled vocabulary for urgency levels of trouble tickets."@en .
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/urgency/ImmediateIntervention> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/urgency> ; rdfs:label "Immediate Intervention"@en .
